net.canarymod.api.entity.living.animal

Interface Horse

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Ageable, AnimalVehicle, Entity, EntityAnimal, EntityLiving, LivingBase, Tameable, Vehicle

    public interface Horse
extends AnimalVehicle, Ageable, Tameable
    Horse wrapper interface

    NOTE: This covers Horses, Donkeys, Mules, Zombie Horses, and Skeleton Horses.
    While Horses can be tame, there is no Owner information, there for does not extends Tameable

    Author:
    Jason (darkdiplomat)
